### Get Auth Token
# @name login
POST {{BACKEND_DOMAIN}}/api/v1/auth/email/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "{{TEST_EMAIL}}",
  "password": "{{TEST_PASSWORD}}"
}

### Set token variable from login response
@token = {{login.token}}

### ===========================================
### STATUS UPDATE ENDPOINTS
### ===========================================

### Update Cost Center Status to Hold
PATCH {{BACKEND_DOMAIN}}/api/v1/cost-centers/7/hold
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Update Cost Center Status to Active
PATCH {{BACKEND_DOMAIN}}/api/v1/cost-centers/7/activate
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Update Cost Center Status to Cancelled
PATCH {{BACKEND_DOMAIN}}/api/v1/cost-centers/7/cancel
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Update Cost Center Status to Hold (Another ID)
PATCH {{BACKEND_DOMAIN}}/api/v1/cost-centers/1/hold
