Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Workflow: Cancel Cost Center
PATCH {{BACKEND_DOMAIN}}/api/v1/cost-centers/10/cancel
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Workflow: Reactivate Cancelled Cost Center
PATCH {{BACKEND_DOMAIN}}/api/v1/cost-centers/10/activate
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

